snippet.title: Diablo IV | Vessel of Hatred | Inside the Game | New Region + Game Features
snippet.description:
The #DiabloIV developers discuss new allies, foes, and features coming in #VesselOfHatred.

🪓 Mercenaries
💀 Dark Citadel
⚔️ Party Finder 
🔥And so much more…

#VesselOfHatred launches on October 8th, pre-purchase the Ultimate Edition today and unlock in-game rewards: diablo.com/expansion
